{"tid":2211601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"ABC News華分部前主管親述逃離過程 14歲女兒險遭牽連","createTime":"2020-09-21T08:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T09:41:26.000Z","uid":241764,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9b3517178594c7d3e555d3f84f9682572d9bdba2","tid":2211601,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:33:29.000Z","msg":"中國上半年至少17名外媒被逐出中國。澳洲ABC News前中國分部主管馬休（Matthew Carney）兩年前離任，周一（21日）他首次公開談及逃亡離開中國的過程。<br />\n<br />\n馬休指，其實每一名在中國工作的外國記者，都受中國政府監控，而中國政府也有意讓你知道你正受監控。他舉例，採訪新疆教育營時，團隊一度遭20名保安人士包圍；深夜時分，又會來敲門「關心」一天行程；網絡也是監控之一，馬休發覺手機被遙控操作&mdash;&mdash;電郵被開啟了，中方監控人員找到一封來自美國社運人士、有關索取六四事件中「坦克人」影片的電郵。馬休睡醒開啟手機時，頁面停留在該電郵，他才發現事件。<br />\n<br />\n馬休稱，他翌日照常工作，可是他認為，如因為調查中國報道而受壓，就是要離開中國的時候<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n談到女兒，馬休怕了起來，與中國當局見面，他問：「與我女兒何干？」中方告知：「你的女兒已經14歲，在中國法律下是一名成人，涉嫌與簽證有關的罪名。」還問他：「你知道我們有權利羈押你的女兒嗎？」馬休提出，「好，我們明天就離開中國。」<br />\n<br />\n馬休於是向澳洲的領事求助。事件最後以馬休跟14歲女兒拍片認罪，承認沒有申請續領簽證作結。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200921/K7DFL35ZYRCT3KGVUJKYGCDOEQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR295nnzWPF7xZ1gI70NWcpCmnuHkMRRayMw23fH5IgQ3dgIbpekcj4optE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200921%2FK7DFL35ZYRCT3KGVUJKYGCDOEQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR295nnzWPF7xZ1gI70NWcpCmnuHkMRRayMw23fH5IgQ3dgIbpekcj4optE&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZokzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=f8d0b94e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200921%2FK7DFL35ZYRCT3KGVUJKYGCDOEQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR295nnzWPF7xZ1gI70NWcpCmnuHkMRRayMw23fH5IgQ3dgIbpekcj4optE&h=7f2010c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200921/K7DFL35ZYRCT3KGVUJKYGCDOEQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR295nnzWPF7xZ1gI70NWcpCmnuHkMRRayMw23fH5IgQ3dgIbpekcj4optE</a>"},{"pid":"fb9ee36acbb37998fd886def35dc767a6d50a32a","tid":2211601,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:40:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33ea140c89fcc25a728e91d74df0e55a28f11d05","tid":2211601,"uid":222970,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"美國左膠又當見唔到"},{"pid":"6dd3c644bfaade518ca7010b59e4d631eef55b08","tid":2211601,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b60a5e522747cf91c05fa3458049bba05676979e","tid":2211601,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:46:07.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫手retweet 樓主pin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mjscarney/status/1307782811399540736?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmjscarney%2Fstatus%2F1307782811399540736%3Fs%3D21&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZokzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=4c0bc8a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmjscarney%2Fstatus%2F1307782811399540736%3Fs%3D21&h=13e6fb89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mjscarney/status/1307782811399540736?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"fb8ba9cdb736842fedef205d7c015d471df741d7","tid":2211601,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:46:57.000Z","msg":"支那比納粹邪惡一萬倍"},{"pid":"19f1bfe5312f70b6610e2e3d1c63c2b0d0fc584f","tid":2211601,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:48:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfc9e9ac382ccdcb28562e4fca7d6488e117d401","tid":2211601,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33ea140c89fcc25a728e91d74df0e55a