 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"左膠：叫我地去支那？不了，唔自由"},{"pid":"31af0c3d825b18cc50cd5f0137433a6bc2a3f1c3","tid":2211601,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e678cd42864595ac17a43b63a4f0f94441a60537","tid":2211601,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b60a5e522747cf91c05fa3458049bba05676979e","tid":2211601,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:46:07.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫手retweet 樓主pin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mjscarney/status/1307782811399540736?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmjscarney%2Fstatus%2F1307782811399540736%3Fs%3D21&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZokzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=4c0bc8a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmjscarney%2Fstatus%2F1307782811399540736%3Fs%3D21&h=13e6fb89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mjscarney/status/1307782811399540736?s=21</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"點解支共威脅奸佢個女都無人講<br />\n<br />\n<em>She knew she had total power over me and she let the words sink in. After some time she added: &quot;I do have to inform you, Mr Carney, that we have a right to <span class=\"red\">keep your daughter in an undisclosed location</span> and I do have to inform you <span class=\"red\">there would be other adults present</span>&quot;.</em>"},{"pid":"a184901daefbbf92145bcbf9cadc99a95b922fa7","tid":2211601,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ef585843da55156b0f0a0c54a6ab8dfaca29ad","tid":2211601,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:38:24.000Z","msg":"18年12月嘅事<br />\n「馬休當年對事件隻字不提，是為了不影響ABC News在中國的運作，不過，ABC News兩名記者Bill Birtles及Mike Smith本月被驅出中國，馬休決定道出陳年事。」<br />\n<br />\n14歲喺法律下就係成人，要拍片認罪<br />\n呢單算好彩畀佢走"},{"pid":"b3e32a7c1a44544942c2c33a5b3647faf62ecd63","tid":2211601,"uid":29555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}